                        <p>RUTERO gives admission to brilliant and intelligent young boys and girls every year, fostering academic excellence and character development.</p>
                        <a href="/admission" class="feature-link">Learn More â†’</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-content">
                        <h3>School Programmes</h3>
                        <p>RUTERO offers your child a great deal of opportunities to explore all possibilities in life through comprehensive educational programs.</p>
