                                <img src="Images/PHOTO-2024-05-01-10-27-35.jpg" alt="Proprietor Message">
                            </div>
                            <div class="announcement-content">
                                <h3>Welcome to Excellence in Education</h3>
                                <div class="article-meta">
                                    <span>by Proprietor</span> â€¢ <span>January 15, 2025</span>
                                </div>
                                <p>At Rutero Model School, we are committed to providing world-class education that nurtures young minds and prepares them for future success. Our dedication to academic excellence remains unwavering.</p>
